CHANGES
=======

* fork repository and update authorship to Tobias Wolf
* change Docker image to towolf/homematicip-exporter
* use python3 instead of python in Makefile
* simplify README for forked project

Changes since upstream/master:

* refactor weather metrics to use dedicated hmip_weather_* prefix
* add extended metrics for floor terminal, weather, and device info
* add vaporAmount, status metrics, and temperatureOffset
* safely access RSSI attributes using getattr
* add RSSI device and peer value metrics
* add channel name label to heating valve position metric
* rename humidity metric to hmip_current_humidity_relative
* handle NoneType for valvePosition in FloorTerminalBlock12
* remove unused PlugableSwitch import
* add separate metric hmip_heating_valve_position for floor terminal blocks
* handle missing asyncio event loop in collector threads
* fix initialization order of Home client
* add support for FALMOT valve positions
* rename temperature metrics to include unit
* rename metric prefix from homematicip to hmip
* remove TemperatureHumiditySensorDisplay code
* remove ShutterContact, HeatingThermostat, TemperatureHumiditySensorOutdoor and TemperatureHumiditySensorWithoutDisplay
* remove SwitchMeasuring code
* refactor to use on-demand collection
* update dependencies and fix breaking changes
* update python version to 3.11
* add unit tests for exporter

* only report if there's something to report
* bump homematicip to 0.10.5
* include events. print default values in help
* fix metric labels
* last\_status\_update metric
* add device metrics, increase collect-interval-seconds to 30
* fix metric namespace
* make latest
